0.21","displayDimension":"0.21 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"au trait carr\u00e9","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":"","note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Eau-forte et burin. Signature grav\u00e9e en bas \u00e0 gauche du trait carr\u00e9 : \u0027Peint par Fran\u00e7ois Boucher.\u0027 et \u00e0 droite : \u0027Grav\u00e9 par Lau. Cars.\u0027. Ensuite la lettre : \u0027La France g\u00e9mit des troubles qui la divisent. La Fid\u00e9lit\u00e9 la console, \u0026 lui pr\u00e9sente des sujets z\u00e9l\u00e9s. L\u0027un d\u0027entre eux tient une grenade, \/ simbole de l\u0027union. Le ciel s\u0027ouvre; le Saint Esprit paroist. Des Genies semblent inspirer l\u0027id\u00e9e d\u0027en instituer un Ordre. L\u0027Ange tut\u00e9laire \/ de la France foudroye les ennemis de l\u0027Etat \u0026 de la Religion, tandis que la Paix \u0026 l\u0027Abondance annoncent des temps plus heureux.\u0027","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Derni\u00e8re provenance : Rothschild, baron Edmond de","note":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"startYear":1935,"endYear":null}]}],"ownedBy":"","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"collection":[{"value":"Roth, David-Didier"}],"place":[{"value":"Lille, Mus\u00e9e des Beaux-Arts, oeuvre en rapport"}],"person":[{"value":"Poullain de Saint-Foix, Germain Fran\u00e7ois+"}],"subject":[{"value":"All\u00e9gorie de l\u0027Abondance"},{"value":"All\u00e9gorie de la Paix"},{"value":"All\u00e9gorie de la France"},{"value":"Saint-Esprit entour\u00e9 d\u0027anges"},{"value":"All\u00e9gorie de la Fid\u00e9lit\u00e9"}],"technic":[{"value":"eau-forte"},{"value":"burin"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/54\/89\/68\/00\/AGO548968-000_PE.jpg","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections